curam.util.tab.impl
Interface DynamicMenuStateLoader

public interface DynamicMenuStateLoader

This class supports determining the state of menu items given a menu bar identifier, a list of menu item identifiers, and the list of loaders associated with a menu bar. Loaders are called. Each can modify the state of a particular menu item. A menu item can have states of enabled or disabled, and visible or hidden.
